posting_body: ['Ask us about our renovations!', 'Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Come home to a resort-inspired apartment community in Plantation, FL.', 'Our apartments offer an oasis with beautiful lake views and great amenities in studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and even three bedroom layouts.', 'You will find the perfect selection of modern floor plans with open-concept layouts.', 'Residents love the convenience of a washer and dryer in their apartment home as well as additional storage availability!', 'Amenities:', '-Conference Room', '-Lake View', '-Screen Patio and Balcony', '-Exterior Storage', '-Dishwasher', '-Two Resort-style Swimming Pools', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Tennis & Basketball Courts', '-Picnic & Barbecue Areas', '-Business Center & Resident Lounge', '-Ceramic Tile Bath', '-Vaulted Ceilings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
